                    </p>
                    <a href="/RapidOpen2025" class="event-button">Learn more + register</a>
                </div>

                <div class="Events-bar" onclick="navigateTo('/QCC2025')" style="background-image: url('images/stauffer.jpg')">
                    <h3>Queen's Chess Championship</h3>
                    <p class="event-details">
                        📍 Queen's University, Kingston, ON<br>
                        📅 March 2nd-3rd <br>
                        📌 CFC rated Tournament<br>
