                        📍 Queen's University, Kingston, ON<br>
                        📅 January 24-26, 2025<br>
                        📌 CFC rated Tournament<br>
                        🏆 CFC rated Team Competition
                    </p>
                    <a href="CUCC2025" class="event-button">Learn more + view results</a>
                </div>
            
                <div class="Events-bar" onclick="navigateTo('/blitzT')" style="background-image: url('images/stauffer.jpg')">
                    <h3>Winter Blitz Tournament</h3>
                    <p class="event-details">
                        📍 Queen's University, Kingston, ON<br>
                        📅 February 8, 2025<br>
                        📌 Ratings based on Chess.com or Lichess.org accounts<br>
                        ⚡ 5-minute games with 3-second increments
                    </p>
                    <a href="/blitzT" class="event-button">Learn more + view results</a>
                </div>
